OL,3,CParents speak of 'constant emptiness'
OL,4,Cafter son's killer jailed
OL,6,FThe parents of murdered model and DJ
OL,7,FLuke Harden have spoken of the
OL,8,Fheartbreak their family now faces
OL,9,Fafter his killer was jailed.
OL,11,FBhekisani Matabiswana attacked Luke on
OL,12,F1 November 2025 as he left a Halloween
OL,13,Fparty, and went on to attempt to flee
OL,14,Fthe country.
OL,16,FMatabiswana, 27, of St James Street in
OL,17,FBacup, was handed a life sentence with
OL,18,Fa minimum term of 16 and a half years
OL,19,Fbefore he is eligible for parole.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
