CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779120674
OL,3,CParents speak of 'constant emptiness'
OL,4,Cafter son's killer jailed
OL,6,FHe was found guilty of murdering the
OL,7,F37-year-old in Rossendale on 1
OL,8,FNovember 2025.
OL,10,FLuke was booked to DJ at the party at
OL,11,Fa working men's club in Huttock End
OL,12,FLane in Stacksteads that Matabiswana
OL,13,Fwas attending.
OL,15,FBoth men left seperately, but CCTV
OL,16,Ffootage captured Matabiswana and his
OL,17,Fgroup ahead of Luke as they walked
OL,18,Fthrough the area.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779120674
OL,3,CParents speak of 'constant emptiness'
OL,4,Cafter son's killer jailed
OL,6,FIt was there that Matabiswana launched
OL,7,Fthe assault on Luke, punching him as
OL,8,Fhe lay defenceless on the ground. Luke
OL,9,Fhad no defensive wounds, and there was
OL,10,Fno evidence to suggest he was the
OL,11,Faggressor, the court heard.
OL,13,FMatabiswana then used Luke's phone to
OL,14,Fcall his friends and family, telling
OL,15,Fthem their loved one was on the floor,
OL,16,Fbut did not call for an ambulance or
OL,17,Foffer first aid.
OL,19,FA passer-by called emergency services
OL,20,Fand tried to help Luke, but he was
OL,21,Fpronounced dead at the scene.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779120674
OL,3,CParents speak of 'constant emptiness'
OL,4,Cafter son's killer jailed
OL,6,FA Home Office post-mortem confirmed
OL,7,FLuke died of blunt force trauma to his
OL,8,Fhead and neck.
OL,10,FMatabiswana attempted to flee the UK,
OL,11,Fbooking a flight to South Africa, but
OL,12,Fwas arrested at Manchester Airport.
OL,14,FHe gave several conflicting accounts
OL,15,Fto police, including claims of self-
OL,16,Fdefence that were rejected by the jury.
OL,18,FHe showed no remorse for his actions,
OL,19,Faccording to police.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
