OL,3,CParents speak of 'constant emptiness'
OL,4,Cafter son's killer jailed
OL,6,FIn a statement read in court, Luke's
OL,7,Ffather Gary Harden said "Since
OL,8,FNovember first, 2025, our lives have
OL,9,Fcompletely changed.
OL,11,F"The pain of losing Luke in such a
OL,12,Fviolent and senseless way is something
OL,13,Fwe carry every single day. There is a
OL,14,Fconstant emptiness that cannot be
OL,15,Ffilled... What hurts most is knowing I
OL,16,Fwill never hear him say 'love you too,
OL,17,FDad' again.
OL,26,@oD@YOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779120674
OL,3,CParents speak of 'constant emptiness'
OL,4,Cafter son's killer jailed
OL,6,F"I will never hug him again, never see
OL,7,Fhis smile, never hear his laugh. That
OL,8,Fhas been taken from me, and from
OL,9,Feveryone who loved him."
OL,11,FLuke's mother, Katie McGovern, said
OL,12,F"The reality of our situation and
OL,13,Ffamily dynamic has now changed
OL,14,Fforever... We have been robbed of
OL,15,Ftime, hugs, kisses, love, memories.
OL,17,F"Watching his life, his future, his
OL,18,Fplans and his career all unfold has
OL,19,Fbeen ripped away and the reason why is
OL,20,Fstill unknown.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@XO]tD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779120674
OL,3,CParents speak of 'constant emptiness'
OL,4,Cafter son's killer jailed
OL,6,F"We have been robbed of a son,
OL,7,Fsomething a parent should never do,
OL,8,Fbury their child in their lifetime."
OL,10,FDetective Inspector Pete MacDonald
OL,11,Fsaid "Luke Harden was the victim of a
OL,12,Fvicious attack carried out by a man
OL,13,Fwho continued to assault him while he
OL,14,Flay defenceless on the ground.
OL,16,F"Matabiswana has shown no remorse
OL,17,Fwhatsoever for his actions and has
OL,18,Fmade several efforts to evade justice,
OL,19,Fincluding by trying to flee the
OL,20,Fcountry.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@dO]sD@FOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
