PN,39208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779120674
OL,3,CParents speak of 'constant emptiness'
OL,4,Cafter son's killer jailed
OL,6,F"While no jail term can ever
OL,7,Fcompensate for the loss of a life, I
OL,8,Fhope it gives Luke's family some sense
OL,9,Fthat justice has been done."
OL,11,FMatabiswana will serve at least
OL,12,Fsixteen and a half years before being
OL,13,Fconsidered for parole.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
